A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering holographic icons float between neon-lit skyscrapers, each icon rendered as a glowing geometric symbol representing different digital functions - a user silhouette, gears, arrows, hearts, and stars cascading down like digital rain. The icons emit soft cyan and magenta light, reflecting off wet streets below. In the foreground, a massive translucent crystal structure houses hundreds of tiny floating symbols arranged in a perfect grid, pulsing with energy. The atmosphere is misty with data particles suspended in the air, creating depth and mystery. Dark purple clouds swirl overhead while the city's chrome architecture gleams with reflected icon light.
